<HL>
   American Barrick Sees Its Gold Output
   Continuing to Grow, Posts Higher Profit
   ----
   By Larry M. Greenberg
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/06/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
<CO>
   ABX NEM NGC T.ABX
</CO>
<MS>
BASIC MATERIALS (BSC)
